  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Pediatric patients ages 0-17

          -  Patients presenting to the University of Michigan for evaluation just before
             undergoing stage 3 of the Fontan operation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients over the age of 17

          -  Patients who have chronic liver disease (elevation of ALT, AST, or Bilirubin greater
             than two times the upper limits of normal &gt;4 weeks)

          -  Patients who have evidence of liver enlargement or nodularity on prior ultrasound
             imaging

          -  Patients who have a history of portal vein or hepatic vein thrombosis

          -  Patients (parents) who are unwilling to read and sign the informed consent document
      </textblock>
